command, command.info in ~/.config/blather will be created after first run
Go to http://www.speech.cs.cmu.edu/tools/lmtool.html upload file sentences.corpus 
Download the *.dic and *.lm files and copy them to config dir 
Commands are configured in commands and command.info files. 
